    "This deployment of facial detection technology significantly boosts road safety by adeptly assessing drivers' drowsiness levels and reducing the risks associated with drowsy driving [62][63][64].Table 2 provides a comprehensive summary of various studies centered on facial classification research, offering a detailed overview of this specific area.Facial Classification entails detecting and analyzing a driver's facial features and expressions, including yawning, blinking, or looking away from the road.",
